name: CoreAPI Security_Role
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Security_Roles details.
about:
Description

Planet 9-Security_Role facilitates to add the new roles which can be added to the user and the groups to provide the Planet 9 artifacts accessibility. 

You can use API Security_Role in your app if you want to add, delete, and update the Role. 

"API Security_Role" is the Planet 9 API to access the Planet 9 "Roles" and the operations performed on them. Also, you can assign the defined "Roles" to the user from the app using "API Security_User" and to the group from "API Security_Group". 

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) and authentication that enables access to the Security_Role API.
